
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Consolidation' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' box is enabled and automatically preselected
And 'I know' box is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and automatically preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

When I am on 'Characterization I' tab
Then 'Lobar' radio button is enabled
And 'Segmental' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled

And 'Positive bronchopneumogram' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ground-Glass Opacity (GGO)' checkbox is enabled

And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Central' radio button is enabled
And 'Miliary pattern/diffuse' radio button is enabled

And 'Extensive' radio button is enabled
And 'Spotted' radio button is enabled

And 'Well-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

When I select 'I know' radio button
Then 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lobar' radio button
Then 'Localization at lobe level*' localizer is enabled
When I click on the localizer
Then canvas opens
When I select all parts on the localizer
Then all parts are selected and turn red

When I close the canvas
And I select 'Segmental' radio button
Then 'Localization at segment level' localizer is enabled
When I click on the localizer
Then canvas opens
When I select all parts on the localizer
Then all parts are selected and turn red

When I select 'Ground-Glass Opacity (GGO)' checkbox
Then 'Single' radio button is enabled
And 'Multiple' radio button is enabled
And 'Dark bronchus sign' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Spotted' radio button
Then 'Confluent' checkbox is enabled
And 'Rounded shape' checkbox is enabled
And 'Geographic appearance' checkbox is enabled
And 'Peribronchovascular' checkbox is enabled
And 'Crazy-paving pattern' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mosaic pattern' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Crazy-paving pattern' checkbox
Then 'Interlobular septal thickening' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Well-defined' radio button
Then 'Volume loss' radio button is enabled
And 'Constant volume' radio button is enabled
And 'Volume increase' radio button is enabled
